data.description:
Welcome to High Point of Delray Section 7, an inviting 55+ community nestled in proximity to the renowned Atlantic Avenue and vibrant downtown Delray Beach. Step into luxury with this welcoming condo that boasts a spacious open floor plan adorned with porcelain tile floors throughout. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring trendy backsplash, high-end appliances, wooden cabinets, king-size bed headboard, a Samsung 4K 65'' TV, a glass dining table and a waterfall-edge quartz countertop illuminated by modern LED lighting. Brand new AC, common laundry back by the patio. This one-bedroom condo has been thoughtfully redesigned with two beautiful new bathrooms. Indulge in a relaxing bubble bath in the luxurious standing tub or opt for a steamy shower in the en-suite bathroom, complete with a large step-in shower stall.

The bedroom is a sanctuary with a roomy walk-in closet that now boasts newly installed built-in and linen cabinets for enhanced organization. The entire home is fortified with hurricane impact windows, ensuring safety and peace of mind. Take in the outdoors from the comfort of your screened-in patio or the inviting outdoor terrace.

This exceptional residence is strategically located just minutes away from upscale shopping, dining, and an array of entertainment options. The community itself is meticulously maintained and offers resort-style amenities including but not limited to: a fitness center, community pool, shuffleboard, pickleball, social events and much more!

Discover the epitome of 55+ living in this elegant and thoughtfully updated condo. Don't miss the chance to call this impressive property your home, where luxury meets tranquility in a well-maintained community.
